# Model Behavior Documentation

This document explains how the AI Support Assistant behaves.

---

## Hallucination Risk

The model may:
- Invent refund policies
- Provide outdated information
- Assume missing context

Mitigation:
- Use retrieval augmentation
- Limit temperature
- Add guardrail prompts

---

## Escalation Logic

The system escalates when:
- Financial disputes occur
- Legal threats appear
- Abusive language is detected

---

## Sensitive Data Handling

The model:
- Does not store personal data
- Does not access payment systems
- Cannot initiate refunds directly
